==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Crustaceous
<hw>Crus*ta"ceous</hw> <pr>(kr?s-t?"sh?s; 97)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[NL. <ets>crustaceous</ets>. See <er>crustacea</er>.]</ety>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>Pertaining to, or of the nature of, crust or shell;
having a crustlike shell.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Belonging to the Crustacea;
crustacean.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Crustaceousness</ent>⟦br⟧
